    "nt": "2",
    "etymologie": "(< <span class=\"greek\">ἀδύνατος</span>), [in LXX: De 17:8, Za 8:6 (<span class=\"hebrew\">פּלא</span> ni.), Jb 42:2 (<span class=\"hebrew\">בּצר</span> ni.), al.;]"
