    "definitie": "<em>to praise</em>: c. acc., <span class=\"greek\">τ. θεόν</span>, Lk 2:13, 20 19:37 24:53, Ac 2:47 3:8, 9, Ro 15:11; c. dat., <span class=\"greek\">τ. Θεῷ</span> (Je 20:13, al. for <span class=\"hebrew\">הִלֵּל לְ</span>; v. Field, <i>Notes</i>, 245), Re 19:5.†",
    "nt": "9",
