    "etymologie": "(< <span class=\"greek\">αἰχμάλωτος</span>), [in LXX chiefly for <span class=\"hebrew\">שׁבה</span>;] in late writers = cl. <span class=\"greek\">αἰχμάλωτον ποιῶ</span> (<span class=\"greek\">ἄγω</span>),"
