    "vorm": "<b>ἄ-κακος</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-ον</span>,",
    "definitie": "<br/>(a) as in cl. (Æsch., Plat., al.), of persons, <em>simple</em>, <em>guileless</em>: Ro 16:18, He 7:26 (cf. Cremer, 327); <br/>(b) of things, <em>undamaged</em> (? MM, <i>VGT</i>, s.v.).†",
