    "definitie": "<em>Alexander</em> <br/>1. Son of Simon of Cyrene: Mk 15:21 <br/>2. A kinsman of the High Priest: Ac 4:6. <br/>3. A certain Jew: Ac 19:33. <br/>4. A coppersmith: I Ti 1:20. <br/>5. Perh. = 4 (v. Ellic. on I Ti 1:20): II Ti 4:14.†",
