    "nt": "216",
    "etymologie": "[in LXX chiefly for <span class=\"hebrew\">אִישׁ</span>, freq. <span class=\"hebrew\">אֱנוֹשׁ</span>, also <span class=\"hebrew\">אָדָם</span>, etc.;]"
