    "definitie": "<em>supreme</em>, <em>a consul</em>, one acting in place of a consul, <em>a proconsul</em>, the administrator of a senatorial province (cf. <span class=\"greek\">ἡγεμών</span>, and v. MM, <i>VGT</i>, 44): Ac 13:7, 8, 12 18:12 19:38.†",
    "nt": "5",
