    "definitie": "<em>an exchange</em>, the price received as an equivalent for an article of commerce: Mt 16:26, Mk 8:37 (cf. Si 26:14; and v. Swete, <i>Mk.</i> 8:37; Cremer, 90).†",
    "nt": "2",
    "etymologie": "(<span class=\"greek\">ἀντί</span>, <span class=\"greek\">ἄλλαγμα</span>; < <span class=\"greek\">ἀλλάσσω</span>), [in LXX chiefly for <span class=\"hebrew\">מְחִיר</span>;]"
