    "nt": "2",
    "etymologie": "(contr. fr. <span class=\"greek\">-όος</span>; < <span class=\"greek\">ἁ.-</span> cop., <span class=\"greek\">πλόος</span>), [in LXX: Pr 11:25*;]"
