    "vorm": "<b>ἀπ-όλλυμι</b> and <b>ἀπολλύω</b>,",
    "definitie": "Act., <br/>(1) <em>to destroy utterly</em>, <em>destroy</em>, <em>kill</em>: Mk 1:24, 9:22, al.; <span class=\"greek\">τ. ψνχήν</span>, Mt 10:28, al.; <br/>(2) <em>to lose utterly</em>: Mt 10:42, al.; metaph., of failing to save, Jo 6:39 18:9.",
    "nt": "90",
