    "vorm": "<b>ἅπτω</b>,",
    "definitie": "prop., <em>to fasten to</em>; hence, of fire, <em>to kindle</em>, <em>light</em>: Lk 8:16 11:33 15:8, Ac 28:2. Mid., c. gen., <em>to fasten oneself to</em>, <em>cling to</em>, <em>lay hold of</em> (so in <span class=\"greek\">π.</span>; MM, s.v.): Mt 8:3, 15, Jo 20:17, al.; of carnal intercourse, I Co 7:1; with reference to levitical and ceremonial prohibitions, II Co 6:17, Col 2:21; of hostile action, I Jo 5:18 (cf. <span class=\"greek\">ἀν-</span>, <span class=\"greek\">καθ-</span>, <span class=\"greek\">περι-</span> <span class=\"greek\">άπτω</span>).",
