    "definitie": "<em>to be idle</em>; <span class=\"greek\">τὸ κρίμα . . . ἀ.</span>, <em>lingers</em> (cf. MGr. <span class=\"greek\">ἀργά</span>, <em>late</em>: MM, s.v.): II Pe 2:3.†",
