    "etymologie": "(< <span class=\"greek\">ἄργυρος</span>), [in LXX for <span class=\"hebrew\">כֶּסֶף</span> (Ge 13:2, al.), exc. La 4:1 (<span class=\"hebrew\">כֶּתֶם</span>);]"
