    "definitie": "<em>bread</em>, <em>a loaf</em>: Mt 4:3, 4, Mk 3:20, al.; <span class=\"greek\">ἄρτοι τ. προθέσεως</span>, <em>bread of the setting forth</em>, i.e. the shewbread. Metaph., <span class=\"greek\">ὁ ἄ. τ. θεοῦ, τ. ζωῆς</span>, ref. to Christ, Jo 6:33, 35; in general, <em>food</em>: Mt 6:11, al.; <span class=\"greek\">ἄ. φαγεῖν</span> (Heb. <span class=\"hebrew\">אֲכֹל לֶחֶם</span>), <em>to eat</em> (MM, s.v.), Lu 14:1, al.",
