    "gloss": "ruler of a synagogue",
    "vorm": "*† <b>ἀρχισυνάγωγος</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-ου, ὁ</span>",
    "definitie": "<em>ruler of a synagogue</em>, an administrative officer, supervising the worship (<span class=\"hebrew\">רֹאשׁ הַכְּנֵםֶת</span>): Mk 5:22, 35, 36, 38, Lk 8:49 13:14, Ac 13:15 18:8, 17 (Inscr., v. MM, s.v.; cf. also <i>DB</i>, <i>ext.</i>, 101).†",
