    "definitie": "<em>Bethesda</em>, a pool in Jerusalem: Jo 5:2, Rec. (<span class=\"greek\">Βηθζαθά</span>, WH, <span class=\"greek\">Βηθσαϊδά</span>, WH, mg.).†",
    "nt": "1",
    "etymologie": "(deriv. uncertain, v. Westc. on Jo 5:2, and <i>DB</i>, i, 279),"
