    "gloss": "to spend life, to live",
    "vorm": "<b>βιόω</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-ῶ</span>",
    "definitie": "<em>to spend life, to live</em>: <span class=\"greek\">τ. χρόνον βιῶσαι</span> (cl., more freq. 2 aor., <span class=\"greek\">-ναι</span>), I Pe 4:2 (cf. Jb, l.c.).†",
