    "gloss": "to sprout",
    "vorm": "<b>βλαστάνω</b>,",
    "definitie": "<br/>1. <em>to sprout</em>: Mt 13:26, Mk 4:27, He 9:4. <br/>2. In late Gk., causal, <em>to make to grow, produce</em>: c. acc., Ja 5:18.†",
