    "definitie": "<em>second</em> in order, with or without idea of time: Mt 22:26, 39, al.; <span class=\"greek\">θάνατος</span>, Re 2:11 20:14 21:8; <span class=\"greek\">χάρις</span>, II Co 1:15. In neut. as adv., <em>secondly, a second time</em>; opp. to <span class=\"greek\">πρῶτον</span>: Jo 3:4 21:16, I Co 12:28, Re 19:3; <span class=\"greek\">τὸ δ.</span>, II Co 13:2, Ju 5; <span class=\"greek\">ἐν τ. δ.</span>, <em>at the second time</em>: Ac 7:13; in later usage (as I Mac 9:1), <span class=\"greek\">ἐκ δ.</span>, Mk 14:72, Jo 9:24, Ac 11:9, He 9:28.",
    "nt": "43"
