    "etymologie": "(< <span class=\"greek\">διδάσκω</span>), [in LXX: Pr 2:17 (<span class=\"hebrew\">אַלּוּף</span>), Is 29:13 (<span class=\"hebrew\">למד</span> pu.), Si 24:33 39:8 * ;]"
