    "vorm": "<b>δύναμαι</b>, depon.,",
    "definitie": "<em>to be able, have power</em>, whether by personal ability, permission, or opportunity: c. inf. (M, <i>Pr.</i>, 205; WM, § 44, 3) pres., Mt 6:24, Mk 2:7, Jo 3:2, I Co 10:21, al.; c. inf. aor., Mt 3:9, Mk 1:45, Jo 3:3, 4 Ro 8:39, al.; c. acc., <em>to be able to do</em> something: Mk 9:22, Lk 12:26; II Co 13:8; absol., <em>to be able, capable, powerful</em>: I Co 3:2 10:13.",
