    "gloss": "to beat level like a threshing floor",
    "vorm": "<b>ἐδαφίζω</b> (< <span class=\"greek\">ἔδαφος</span>)",
    "definitie": "<br/>1. <em>to beat level like a threshing floor</em> (Theophr.). <br/>2. <em>to dash to the ground</em> (Field, <i>Notes</i>, 74): Lk 19:44 (cf. Ps 136 (137):9, Ho 14:1).†",
