    "definitie": "<em>an idol's temple</em>: I Co 8:10 (cf. <span class=\"greek\">Ἀσταρτεῖον</span>, I Ki 31:10; v. <i>ICC</i>, in I Co, l.c.).†",
    "nt": "1",
