    "vorm": "<b>ἱκετήριος</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-α, -ον</span>",
    "definitie": "<em>of a suppliant</em>; as subst., <span class=\"greek\">ἡ ἱ.</span> (sc. <span class=\"greek\">ῥάβδος</span>), <br/>1. in cl., <em>an olive-branch</em>, carried by a suppliant. <br/>2. In late Gk. = <span class=\"greek\">ἱκεσία</span>, <em>supplication</em>: pl., <span class=\"greek\">δεήσεις κ. ἱ.</span>, He 5:7.",
