    "gloss": "a garment",
    "vorm": "<b>ἱμάτιον</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-ου, τό</span>",
    "definitie": "<em>a garment</em>, but in usage always (exc. in p1., v. infr.) of an outer garment, <em>a mantle</em>, <em>cloak</em> (thrown over the <span class=\"greek\">χιτών</span>; v. Rutherford, <i>NPhr.</i>, 22; <i>DCG</i>, i, 499<sup>a</sup>): Mt 9:16, 20, 21, Mk 2:21 5:27, 28, 30, Jo 19:2, Ac 12:8, al.; opp. to <span class=\"greek\">χιτών</span>, Mt 5:40, Lk 6:29, Ac 9:39; pl., <em>garments</em>, <em>clothes</em> (i.e. the cloak and the tunic), Mt 17:2 26:65 27:31, 35, Mk 5:30 15:20, 24, Jo 19:23, 24, Ja 5:2, al.",
