    "etymologie": "(dim. of <span class=\"greek\">εἷμα</span>, <i>a garment</i>), [in LXX chiefly for <span class=\"hebrew\">בֶּגֶד</span>, also for <span class=\"hebrew\">שִׂמְלָה</span>, <span class=\"hebrew\">שַׂלְמָה</span>, etc.;]"
