    "nt": "5",
    "etymologie": "(for <span class=\"greek\">καθ’ ἅ</span>), [in LXX: Ge 7:9 19:8, al. (<span class=\"hebrew\">כַּאֲשֶׁר</span>, <span class=\"hebrew\">כְּ</span>), Is 58:11, Wi 3:10, al. ;]"
