    "definitie": "<em>fruit</em>: of trees, Mt 12:33 21:19, Mk 11:14, Lk 6:44 13:6, 7; of vines, Mt 21:34, Mk 12:2, Lk 20:10, I Co 9:7; of fields, Mk 4:29, Lk 12:17, II Ti 2:6, Ja 5:7; <span class=\"greek\">βλαστάνειν</span>, Ja 5:18; <span class=\"greek\">ποιεῖν</span> (cf. <i>Heb.</i> <span class=\"hebrew\">עָשָׂה פְּרִי</span>), Mt 3:10 7:17-19 13:26, Lk 3:9 6:43 8:8 13:9, Re 22:2; <span class=\"greek\">διδόναι</span>, Mt 13:8, Mk 4:7, 8; <span class=\"greek\">φέρειν</span>, Mt 7:18, Jo 12:24 15:2, 4, 5, 8, 16; <span class=\"greek\">ἀποδιδόναι</span>, Mt 21:41, Re 22:2; <span class=\"greek\">ὁ κ. τ. κοιλίας</span> (<span class=\"hebrew\">פְּרִי בֶּטֶן</span>, De 28:4), Lk 1:42; <span class=\"greek\">τ. ὀσφύος</span> (Ge 30:2, al.), Ac 2:30.",
