    "vorm": "<b>κατα-δικάζω</b>,",
    "definitie": "<em>to pass sentence upon</em>, <em>condemn</em>; in cl., c. gen. pers. (acc. rei); in late writers (so LXX), c. acc. pers. (<span class=\"greek\">θανάτῳ</span>, Wi 2:20): Mt 12:7, Ja 5:6; absol. (as Plat., <i>Legg.</i>, 958c), Lk 6:37; pass., Mt 12:37, Lk 6:37.†",
