    "gloss": "to urge on",
    "vorm": "** <b>κελεύω</b>,",
    "definitie": "<em>to urge on</em>, <em>bid</em> by word of mouth, <em>order</em>, <em>command</em> (mostly of one in authority): c. acc. et. inf. aor., Mt 14:19, 28 18:25 27:64, Lk 18:40, Ac 4:15 5:34 8:38 22:30 23:10 25:6, 17; with ellipse of acc., Mt 8:18 14:9 27:58, Ac 12:19 21:33; c. acc. et. inf. Pres., Ac 21:34 22:24 23:3, 35 25:21 27:43; with ellipse of acc., Ac 16:22; ptcp. aor., Ac 25:23.†",
