    "nt": "4",
    "etymologie": "(< <span class=\"greek\">κεντέω</span>, <i>to prick</i>), [in LXX: Pr 26:3 (<span class=\"hebrew\">מֶתֶג</span>), Ho 13:14 (<span class=\"hebrew\">קֹטֶב</span>), 5:12, Si 38:25, IV Mac 14:19*;]"
