    "vorm": "<b>μαθητής</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-οῦ, ὁ</span> (<span class=\"greek\">μανθάνω</span>),",
    "definitie": "<em>a disciple</em>: opp. to <span class=\"greek\">διδάσκαλος</span>, Mt 10:24, Lk 6:40; <span class=\"greek\">Ἰωάννου</span>, Mt 9:14, Lk 7:18, Jo 3:25; <span class=\"greek\">τ. Φαρισαίων</span>, Mt 22:16, Mk 2:18, Lk 5:33; <span class=\"greek\">Μωυσέως</span>, Jo 9:28; <span class=\"greek\">Ἰησοῦ</span>, Lk 6:17 7:11 19:37, Jo 6:66 7:3 19:38; esp. the twelve, Mt 10:1 11:1, Mk 7:17, Lk 8:9, Jo 2:2, al.; later, of Christians generally, Ac 6:1, 2, 7 9:19, al.; <span class=\"greek\">τ. κυρίου</span>, Ac 9:1.",
    "nt": "261",
    "etymologie": "[in LXX only as v.l. (A) in Je 13:21 20:11 26 (46):9*;]"
