    "gloss": "Methuselah",
    "vorm": "<b>Μαθουσάλα</b> (WH, <span class=\"greek\">-αλά</span>), <span class=\"greek\">ὁ</span> (Heb. <span class=\"hebrew\">מְתוּשֶׁלַח</span>),",
    "definitie": "<em>Methuselah</em>: Lk 3:37.†",
