    "definitie": "<em>black</em>: Re 6:5, 12; opp. to <span class=\"greek\">λευκός</span>, Mt 5:36; neut., <span class=\"greek\">τὸ μ.</span>, <em>ink</em> : II Co 3:3, II Jo 12, III Jo 13.†",
