    "vorm": "<b>Μεσσίας</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-ου, ὁ</span> (Aram. <span class=\"hebrew\">מְשִׁיחָא</span> = Heb. <span class=\"hebrew\">מָשִׁיחַ</span> = <span class=\"greek\">Χριστός</span>, q.v.),",
