    "etymologie": "(also <span class=\"greek\">-ος, -ον</span>), [in LXX: Le 19:13 A 25:50, Jb 7:1 (<span class=\"hebrew\">שָׂכִיר</span>), To 5:11, Si 7:10 31 (34):22 37:11*;]"
