    "vorm": "<b>μνᾶ</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-ᾶς, ἡ</span>",
    "definitie": "<em>a mina</em> (Lat.), mna, in Attic a weight and sum of money = 100 <span class=\"greek\">δραχμαί</span> (q.v.): Lk 19:13, 16, 18, 20, 24, 25.†",
