    "vorm": "† <b>μοιχαλίς</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-ίδος, ἡ</span>",
    "definitie": "<em>an adulteress</em>: Ro 7:3; meton., for <span class=\"greek\">μοιχεία</span>, II Pe 2:14. Metaph., of infidelity to God (cf. Ez 16:15 ff. Ez 23:43 ff., al.), Ja 4:4; as an adj., Mt 12:39 16:4, Mk 8:8.†",
