    "etymologie": "(< <span class=\"greek\">ὄκνος</span>, <i>shrinking</i>, <i>hesitation</i>), [in LXX: Nu 22:16 (<span class=\"hebrew\">מנע</span> ni.), Jg 18:9 (<span class=\"hebrew\">עצל</span> ni.), To 12:6, 13, Jth 12:13, Si 7:35, IV Mac 14:4*;]"
