    "definitie": "<em>to be by</em>, <em>at hand</em> or <em>present</em>; <br/>(a) of persons: Re 17:8; <span class=\"greek\">παρών</span> (opp. to <span class=\"greek\">ἀπών</span>), I Co 5:3, II Co 10:2, 11 13:2, 10; seq. <span class=\"greek\">ἐπί</span>, c. gen., Ac 24:19; <span class=\"greek\">ἐνώπιον</span>, Ac 10:33; <span class=\"greek\">ἐνθάδε</span>, Ac 17:6; <span class=\"greek\">πρός</span>, c. acc. pers., Ac 12:20, II Co 11:8, Ga 4:18, 20; <br/>(b) of things: of time, <span class=\"greek\">ὁ καιρός</span>, Jo 7:6; <span class=\"greek\">τ. παρόν</span>, He 12:11; <span class=\"greek\">ἡ ἀλήθεια</span>, II Pe 1:12; <span class=\"greek\">ταῦτα</span>, II Pe 1:9; <span class=\"greek\">τ. παρόντα</span>, He 13:5.",
