    "gloss": "to thicken",
    "vorm": "<b>παχύνω</b>",
    "definitie": "<em>to thicken</em>, <em>fatten</em>; pass., <em>to grow fat</em>. Metaph., <em>to make dull</em> or <em>stupid</em> (<span class=\"greek\">τ. ψυχάς</span>, Plut.); pass., <em>to wax gross</em>: <span class=\"greek\">ἡ καρδία</span>, Mt 13:15, Ac 28:27 (LXX).†",
