    "vorm": "<b>ῥιζόω</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-ῶ</span>",
    "definitie": "<em>to cause to take root</em>. Metaph., <em>to plant, fix firmly, establish</em>: pass. (EV, <i>rooted</i>), <span class=\"greek\">ἐν ἀγάπῃ</span>, Eph 3:18 (17) ; <span class=\"greek\">ἐν Χριστῷ</span>, Col 2:7 (cf. <span class=\"greek\">ἐκ</span> <span class=\"greek\">ριζόω</span>).†",
    "nt": "2",
    "etymologie": "(< <span class=\"greek\">ῥίζα</span>), [in LXX: Is 40:24, Je 12:2 (<span class=\"hebrew\">שׁרשׁ</span>), Si 3:28 24:12 * ;]"
