    "gloss": "to quench",
    "vorm": "<b>σβέννυμι </b>",
    "definitie": "of fire or things on fire, <em>to quench</em>: c. acc, Mt 12:20, Eph 6:16, He 11:34; pass., Mt 25:8, Mk 9:[44, 46], 48, Metaph. (cf. Ca 8:7, IV Mac 16:4): <span class=\"greek\">τὸ πνεῦμα</span>, I Th 5:19.†",
