    "definitie": "<em>to be silent or still, keep silence</em>: Mt 20:31 26:63, Mk 3:4 9:34 10:48 14:61, Lk 19:4 , Ac 18:9; of one dumb, Lk 1:20 (cf. IV Mac 10:18); addressed rhetorically to the sea, <span class=\"greek\">σιώπα</span>, Mk 4:39.†",
