    "gloss": "to sow",
    "vorm": "* <b>σπείρω</b>",
    "definitie": "<em>to sow</em> (seed): absol., Mt 6:26 13:3, 4, 18 25:24, 26, Mk 4:3, 4, Lk 8:5 12:24, Jo 4:36, II Co 9:10; c. acc. rei, Mt 13:24, 27, 37, 39, Mk 4:32, Lk 8:5, I Co 15:36, 37; seq. <span class=\"greek\">εἰς</span>, Mt 13:22, Mk 4:18; <span class=\"greek\">ἐν</span>, Mt 13:24, 31; <span class=\"greek\">ἐπί</span>, c. gen., Mk 4:31; <span class=\"greek\">ἐπί</span>, c. acc, Mt 13:20, 23, Mk 4:16, 20; <span class=\"greek\">παρά</span>, c. acc., Mt 13:19. Metaph.: I Co 9:11 15:42-44, Ga 6:7, 8, Ja 3:18; in proverbial sayings, Mt 25:24, 26, Lk 19:21, 22, Jo 4:37, II Co 9:6, Ga 6:7; in interpretation of parables, Mt 13:19-23, Mk 4:14-20 †",
