    "definitie": "<em>to fix, set fast, make fast</em>: Lk 16:26; <span class=\"greek\">τ. πρόσωτον</span> (Ez 6:2 13:17, al.; v. Dalman, <i>Words</i>, 30 f.), Lk 9:51. Metaph., <em>to confirm, establish</em>: c., acc., Lk 22:32, Ac 18:23, Ro 1:11 16:25, I Th 3:2, 13, II Th 3:3, Ja 5:8, I Pe 5:10, Re 3:2; id. seq. <span class=\"greek\">ἐν</span>, II Th 2:17, II Pe 1:12.†",
    "nt": "13",
    "etymologie": "[in LXX for <span class=\"hebrew\">סמך</span>, <span class=\"hebrew\">שׂוּם</span> (<span class=\"hebrew\">שׂים</span>), etc. ;]"
