    "definitie": "used of the general, <em>to make war, do battle</em>, and (chiefly) of the soldiers serving under him, <em>to serve as a soldier</em>: Lk 3:14, I Co 9:7, II Ti 2:4. Metaph. (cf. MM, ii, xxiii), of spiritual conflict, <em>to war, make war</em>: II Co 10:3, I Ti 1:18, Ja 4:1, I Pe 2:11.†",
