    "gloss": "set over against, opposite",
    "vorm": "<b>ὑπ-εναντίος</b>, <span class=\"greek\">-α, -ον </span>",
    "definitie": "<em>set over against, opposite</em>. Metaph. (Plat., Arist., al.), <em>opposed to, contrary to</em>: c. dat. pers., Col 2:14; absol., as subst., <span class=\"greek\">ὁ ὑ.</span>, He 10:27 (cf. Is 26:11).†",
