    "definitie": "<em>light</em> (opp. to <span class=\"greek\">τὸ σκότος, ἡ σκοτία</span>): Mt 17:2, 5, Jo 11:9, 10, II Co 4:6; <span class=\"greek\">ἡλίου</span>, Re 22:5; of a lamp, Lk 8:16 11:33, Jo 5:35, Re 18:23; of a supernatural heavenly light, Ac 9:3 12:7 22:6, 9, 11 26:13; hence, <span class=\"greek\">ἄγγελος φωτός</span>, II Co 11:14; <span class=\"greek\">ὁ κλήρος τ. ἁγίων ἐν τ. φ.</span>, Col 1:12; of the divine glory, Re 21:24; by meton., of that which gives light: of fire, Mk 14:54, Lk 22:56 (cl.; I Mac 12:29; cf. <i>DCG</i>, i, 595); pl., of a lamp or torch, Ac 16:29; of heavenly bodies, Ja 1:17.",
