    "nt": "74",
    "etymologie": "[in LXX for <span class=\"hebrew\">שָׂמַח</span> (Ge 45:16, al.), <span class=\"hebrew\">גִּיל</span> (Pr 2:14, al.), etc.; inf., as greeting (v. infr.), Is 48:22 57:21 <span class=\"hebrew\">שָׁלוֹם</span>), I Mac 10:18, II Mac 1:1 and freq. in these books ;]"
